(174, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"H\\u00ecnh th\\u00e0nh doanh nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1eeb ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng khai th\\u00e1c t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 t\\u1ea1i vi\\u1ec7n, tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc\",\"slug\":\"hinh-thanh-doanh-nghiep-khoi-nghiep-tu-truong-dai-hoc\",\"slug_id\":\"90\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"M\\u1ed9t \\u0111i\\u1ec1u r\\u00f5 r\\u00e0ng l\\u00e0 \\u1edf b\\u1ea5t k\\u1ef3 qu\\u1ed1c gia n\\u00e0o, tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u lu\\u00f4n l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ea7u ngu\\u1ed3n s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o ra tri th\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi. Th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf ch\\u1ee9ng minh nhi\\u1ec1u tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u tr\\u00ean th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u1ee7 y\\u1ebfu d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean ngu\\u1ed3n thu t\\u1eeb vi\\u1ec7c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Theo s\\u1ed1 li\\u1ec7u th\\u1ed1ng k\\u00ea h\\u1eb1ng n\\u0103m c\\u1ee7a C\\u1ee5c S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7, m\\u1eb7c d\\u00f9 \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam v\\u1eabn chi\\u1ebfm t\\u1ec9 l\\u1ec7 th\\u1ea5p so v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf n\\u1ed9p t\\u1ea1i Vi\\u1ec7t Nam nh\\u01b0ng s\\u1ed1 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u c\\u00f3 xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u0103ng trong nh\\u1eefng n\\u0103m g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00e2y. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t d\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u00e1ng m\\u1eebng, ph\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0o th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n v\\u1ec1 gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u. C\\u00f3 c\\u0103n c\\u1ee9 x\\u00e1c l\\u1eadp quy\\u1ec1n s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 th\\u00ec c\\u00e1c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u n\\u00e0y m\\u1edbi c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 t\\u00e1i \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 cho nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u khoa h\\u1ecdc.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Tuy nhi\\u00ean, c\\u0169ng kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 ph\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eadn r\\u1eb1ng c\\u00f2n t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ea5t c\\u1eadp trong m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh hi\\u1ec7n h\\u00e0nh, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 l\\u00e0 r\\u00e0o c\\u1ea3n cho vi\\u1ec7c th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 c\\u1ee7a tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u. \\u00d4ng \\u0110inh H\\u1eefu Ph\\u00ed, C\\u1ee5c tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng C\\u1ee5c S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u00e3 th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ec1 vi\\u1ec7c ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch, ph\\u00e1p lu\\u1eadt nh\\u1eb1m t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i cho vi\\u1ec7c khai th\\u00e1c, th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a c\\u00e1c k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u c\\u1ee7a tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><em><i><span>&nbsp;D\\u1ef1 th\\u1ea3o Lu\\u1eadt s\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ed5i, b\\u1ed5 sung m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u c\\u1ee7a Lu\\u1eadt S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ec1 xu\\u1ea5t \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh nh\\u1eb1m khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch t\\u1ea1o ra, khai th\\u00e1c t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 do Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0. Xin \\u00f4ng chia s\\u1ebb v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ec1 xu\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c n\\u00eau ra trong D\\u1ef1 th\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 n\\u00e0y v\\u00e0 \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ea1i bi\\u1ec3u qu\\u1ed1c h\\u1ed9i v\\u1ec1 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n \\u0111\\u1ec1 xu\\u1ea5t?<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Lu\\u1eadt S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Qu\\u1ed1c h\\u1ed9i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc C\\u1ed9ng h\\u00f2a x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee7 ngh\\u0129a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam th\\u00f4ng qua n\\u0103m 2005 c\\u00f3 hi\\u1ec7u l\\u1ef1c thi h\\u00e0nh t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 01\\/7\\/2006, \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ed5i, b\\u1ed5 sung hai l\\u1ea7n v\\u00e0o n\\u0103m 2009 v\\u00e0 n\\u0103m 2019,&nbsp; l\\u00e0 v\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n ph\\u00e1p lu\\u1eadt quan tr\\u1ecdng, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh c\\u00e1c quan h\\u1ec7 x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn lo\\u1ea1i t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t - t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7. &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Qua th\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ec5n h\\u01a1n 16 n\\u0103m thi h\\u00e0nh, Lu\\u1eadt S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 \\u0111\\u00e3 ph\\u00e1t huy vai tr\\u00f2 to l\\u1edbn trong vi\\u1ec7c t\\u1ea1o h\\u00e0nh lang ph\\u00e1p l\\u00fd cho ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, x\\u00e1c l\\u1eadp, khai th\\u00e1c, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 th\\u1ee5 h\\u01b0\\u1edfng c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng c\\u1ee7a quy\\u1ec1n s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi t\\u1ea1o m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00e0nh m\\u1ea1nh cho ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh; g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o; \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh chuy\\u1ec3n giao c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7, thu h\\u00fat \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ngo\\u00e0i, qua \\u0111\\u00f3 th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh \\u0111\\u00f3, Lu\\u1eadt S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng \\u0111\\u01b0a h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng b\\u1ea3o h\\u1ed9 s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u1ea1t chu\\u1ea9n m\\u1ef1c theo Hi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 c\\u00e1c kh\\u00eda c\\u1ea1nh li\\u00ean quan t\\u1edbi th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i c\\u1ee7a quy\\u1ec1n SHTT (TRIPS) c\\u1ee7a T\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i Th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi (WTO), c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u00e1p \\u1ee9ng c\\u00e1c ngh\\u0129a v\\u1ee5 theo cam k\\u1ebft c\\u1ee7a Vi\\u1ec7t Nam trong c\\u00e1c hi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ecbnh th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i t\\u1ef1 do (FTA) th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi g\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u00e2y.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Tuy nhi\\u00ean, v\\u1edbi xu th\\u1ebf h\\u1ed9i nh\\u1eadp qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf s\\u00e2u r\\u1ed9ng th\\u00f4ng qua vi\\u1ec7c gia nh\\u1eadp c\\u00e1c \\u0111i\\u1ec1u \\u01b0\\u1edbc qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c hi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ecbnh th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i t\\u1ef1 do th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi, Vi\\u1ec7t Nam ph\\u1ea3i th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c ngh\\u0129a v\\u1ee5 m\\u00e0 m\\u00ecnh cam k\\u1ebft khi gia nh\\u1eadp, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng ngh\\u0129a v\\u1ee5 v\\u1ec1 s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7. Lu\\u1eadt S\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng s\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ed5i ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u t\\u1ea5t y\\u1ebfu. Trong s\\u1ed1 b\\u1ea3y nh\\u00f3m ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch trong l\\u1ea7n s\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ed5i n\\u00e0y, c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch li\\u00ean quan tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, vi\\u1ec7n nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u, c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 l\\u00e0 ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch \\u201cKhuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch t\\u1ea1o ra, khai th\\u00e1c v\\u00e0 ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o ra t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc\\u201d.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>N\\u1ed9i dung s\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ed5i \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7n theo hai ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>- Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n 1 l\\u00e0 s\\u1eeda \\u0111\\u1ed5i \\u0110i\\u1ec1u 86, b\\u1ed5 sung c\\u00e1c \\u0110i\\u1ec1u 86a, 133a, 136a v\\u00e0 kho\\u1ea3n 6 \\u0110i\\u1ec1u 139 \\u0111\\u1ec3 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 v\\u1ec1 vi\\u1ec7c quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed l\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 KH&amp;CN s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trao cho t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u00ec m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1ch t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed3i ho\\u00e0n, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh b\\u1ea3o l\\u01b0u quy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 ngh\\u0129a v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u00ec.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u01b0a ra nh\\u1eb1m m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00edch: (i) t\\u1ea1o \\u0111\\u1ed9ng l\\u1ef1c khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u00ec th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 KH&amp;CN&nbsp; s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd x\\u00e1c l\\u1eadp quy\\u1ec1n SHCN \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi ph\\u1ea7n k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng b\\u1ea3o h\\u1ed9 SHCN, v\\u00e0 th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng quy\\u1ec1n SHCN \\u0111\\u00f3; (ii) v\\u1eabn b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ea3m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ef1 qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd c\\u1ee7a Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u KHCN \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea3o h\\u1ed9 SHCN c\\u00f3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u qu\\u1ed1c gia th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n nh\\u1eb1m th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u KH&amp;CN, th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u ph\\u1ee5c v\\u1ee5 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i, c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111i \\u0111\\u1ea7u l\\u00e0 Hoa K\\u1ef3, ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c n\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u01b0 Anh, Nh\\u1eadt B\\u1ea3n, H\\u00e0n Qu\\u1ed1c, \\u0110\\u1ee9c, \\u00c1o, \\u0110an M\\u1ea1ch, Th\\u1ee5y \\u0110i\\u1ec3n, T\\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ph\\u1ea7n Lan, Nga,\\u2026; c\\u00e1c qu\\u1ed1c gia ch\\u00e2u \\u00c1 nh\\u01b0 \\u1ea4n \\u0110\\u1ed9, Malaysia, Indonesia, Th\\u00e1i Lan, Phillipines v\\u00e0 ch\\u00e2u l\\u1ee5c kh\\u00e1c nh\\u01b0 Brazil, Chile, Mexico, Argentina, Nam Phi, \\u00dac... c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1. Trong s\\u1ed1 50 qu\\u1ed1c gia d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ea7u v\\u1ec1 t\\u1ed5ng s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a c\\u00f4ng d\\u00e2n n\\u0103m 2019, c\\u00f3 24 qu\\u1ed1c gia c\\u00f3 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ph\\u00e1p lu\\u1eadt t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1 Lu\\u1eadt Bayh-Dole c\\u1ee7a Hoa K\\u1ef3. Ngay trong ASEAN, c\\u00f3 4 qu\\u1ed1c gia \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ef1. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t, Lu\\u1eadt Ti\\u1ebfn b\\u1ed9 KH&amp;CN C\\u1ed9ng h\\u00f2a nh\\u00e2n d\\u00e2n Trung Hoa n\\u0103m 2007 c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u00e3 quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh trao quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o ra t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc cho t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u00ec nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 KH&amp;CN.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>&nbsp;- Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n 2 l\\u00e0 gi\\u1eef nguy\\u00ean quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ph\\u00e1p lu\\u1eadt hi\\u1ec7n h\\u00e0nh. Tuy nhi\\u00ean ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eefng t\\u1ed3n t\\u1ea1i sau \\u0111\\u00e2y:<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Ph\\u00e1p lu\\u1eadt hi\\u1ec7n h\\u00e0nh (\\u0110i\\u1ec1u 86 Lu\\u1eadt SHTT, \\u0110i\\u1ec1u 9 Ngh\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ecbnh 103\\/2006\\/N\\u0110-CP) quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ea1o ra tr\\u00ean c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 thu\\u1ed9c v\\u1ec1 Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc. T\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c, c\\u01a1 quan nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c giao quy\\u1ec1n ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 c\\u00f3 tr\\u00e1ch nhi\\u1ec7m \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd n\\u00e0y<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Tuy nhi\\u00ean t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c, c\\u01a1 quan nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c giao quy\\u1ec1n ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd v\\u00e0 tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh ch\\u1ee7 v\\u0103n b\\u1eb1ng b\\u1ea3o h\\u1ed9 th\\u00ec c\\u0169ng kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u1ea3o h\\u1ed9 do kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9c n\\u0103ng c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng kinh doanh.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:white;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:200;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:15pt;margin:6pt 0in;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:black;\\\"><span>Trong tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u00ec c\\u00f3 quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed th\\u00ec c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 quan qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c\\u1ea7n th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n vi\\u1ec7c giao quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 KH&amp;CN. Do t\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5t ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p c\\u1ee7a t\\u00e0i s\\u1ea3n tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u00e1c quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh gi\\u00e1 c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng n\\u00e0y m\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7n nay vi\\u1ec7c giao quy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed v\\u1eabn g\\u1eb7p r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n. V\\u00ec v\\u1eady vi\\u1ec7c gi\\u1eef nguy\\u00ean quy \\u0111\\u1ecbnh hi\\u1ec7n h\\u00e0nh s\\u1ebd kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ec3 gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea5t c\\u1eadp hi\\u1ec7n nay do kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ee7 c\\u0103n c\\u1ee9 ph\\u00e1p l\\u00fd cho t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u00ec th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd s\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ebf, ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ed l\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 KH&amp;CN s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng ng\\u00e2n s\\u00e1ch nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p; kh\\u00f4ng th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1