\\u00ean \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng, ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n; Tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kinh doanh. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, ch\\u00e2n dung nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng, th\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec3u nh\\u1eefng&nbsp;kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n m\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c startup g\\u1eb7p ph\\u1ea3i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px auto;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ph\\u00f3 B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n L\\u00ea C\\u00f4ng H\\u00f9ng cho bi\\u1ebft, ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh nh\\u1eb1m h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn, hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 nh\\u1eefng ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0 k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;