(190, 1, 'tag', '{\"name\":\"Nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\",\"slug\":\"hoat-dong-ho-tro-sinh-vien-khoi-nghiep\",\"slug_id\":\"84\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"V\\u1edbi m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u01b0a c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn g\\u1ea7n h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 truy\\u1ec1n ngu\\u1ed3n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng l\\u1edbn, t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 19-4, V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng (DNES) tri\\u1ec3n khai ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd cho ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cB\\u1ec7 ph\\u00f3ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d d\\u00e0nh cho \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean n\\u0103m 2022. Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh do Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p DNES t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 23, 24-4-2022.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tham gia l\\u00e0 t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 sinh vi\\u00ean y\\u00eau th\\u00edch kinh doanh, kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111ang theo h\\u1ecdc t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 25