(191, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Ph\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u201cKh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 trong sinh vi\\u00ean\\u201d l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 hai\",\"slug\":\"cuoc-thi-khoi-nghiep-cong-nghe-trong-sinh-vien-lan-thu-hai\",\"slug_id\":\"87\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"Nh\\u1eb1m \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 v\\u00e0 th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y c\\u00e1c s\\u00e1ng ki\\u1ebfn kinh doanh, kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p cho \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean, t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 25-3, H\\u1ed9i sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0110\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng (\\u0110H\\u0110N) ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p S\\u1edf Khoa h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u201cKh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 trong sinh vi\\u00ean\\u201d l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 hai (Innovative Technology Entrepreneurship the University of Danang 2022) trong \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng d\\u1ef1 thi l\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean, h\\u1ecdc sinh hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111ang h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0110\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, Cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng, Trung c\\u1ea5p, Ph\\u1ed5 th\\u00f4ng trung h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng. C\\u00e1c th\\u00ed sinh \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd d\\u1ef1 thi theo h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ed9i nh\\u00f3m (m\\u1ed7i \\u0111\\u1ed9i, nh\\u00f3m c\\u00f3 05 ho\\u1eb7c 07 th\\u00e0nh vi\\u00ean) v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd duy nh\\u1ea5t 01 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch c\\u00e1c \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean, h\\u1ecdc sinh hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111ang h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng ngo\\u00e0i th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng tham gia v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9i nh\\u00f3m c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecdc sinh\\/sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0111ang h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp t\\u1ea1i \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng v\\u1edbi s\\u1ed1 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng kh\\u00f4ng qu\\u00e1 03 th\\u00e0nh vi\\u00ean ngo\\u00e0i\\/\\u0111\\u1ed9i nh\\u00f3m; Khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch, \\u01b0u ti\\u00ean c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9i thi c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 tham gia h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn c\\u1ee7a gi\\u1ea3ng vi\\u00ean, gi\\u00e1o vi\\u00ean ho\\u1eb7c c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n m\\u00f4n li\\u00ean quan.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">C\\u00e1c d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p tham d\\u1ef1 cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u201cKh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 trong sinh vi\\u00ean\\u201d ph\\u1ea3i h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 c\\u1ee7a c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed9t ph\\u00e1 \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf, x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i; khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch c\\u00e1c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng, d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n d\\u1ef1 thi c\\u00f3 \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 ti\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfn, hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eb1m t\\u1ea1o ra s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u00e1p \\u1ee9ng nhu c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng trong c\\u00e1c l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c nh\\u01b0: Gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c, y t\\u1ebf; N\\u00f4ng, l\\u00e2m, ng\\u01b0 nghi\\u1ec7p; D\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5, du l\\u1ecbch; T\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh, ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng; Kinh doanh t\\u1ea1o t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i; C\\u00e1c ng\\u00e0nh ngh\\u1ec1 kh\\u00e1c v\\u00e0 l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c kinh doanh kh\\u00e1c\\u2026<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c nh\\u1eadn h\\u1ed3 s\\u01a1 v\\u00e0 b\\u00e0i d\\u1ef1 thi t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 25-3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn 3-4-2022. Sau \\u0111\\u00f3, Ban Gi\\u00e1m kh\\u1ea3o ch\\u1ea5m v\\u00e0 l\\u1ef1a ch\\u1ecdn 25-30 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t v\\u00e0o V\\u00f2ng \\u0110\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n. K\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c Ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ean Fanpage c\\u1ee7a Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 11-4-2022.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">T\\u1ea1i V\\u00f2ng \\u0110\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 12-4 \\u0111\\u1ebfn ng\\u00e0y 24-4-2022, H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0110H\\u0110N ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh tri\\u1ec3n khai h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 cho m\\u1ed7i nh\\u00f3m ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n v\\u00e0 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m cho c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn l\\u1ef1a tham d\\u1ef1 v\\u00f2ng Chung k\\u1ebft.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ban T\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c s\\u1ebd t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u00f2ng ch\\u1ea5m\\/b\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ecdn ra 15 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng t\\u1ed1t nh\\u1ea5t. Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, ch\\u1ecdn 06 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i \\u0111i th\\u1eb3ng v\\u00e0o v\\u00f2ng chung k\\u1ebft; 09 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i s\\u1ebd l\\u1ea5y \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn b\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ecdn t\\u1eeb c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1c c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n, nh\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c th\\u1ea7y, c\\u00f4 gi\\u00e1o, c\\u00e1c \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, thanh ni\\u00ean quan t\\u00e2m \\u0111\\u1ec3 ch\\u1ecdn ra 04 \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i v\\u00e0o V\\u00f2ng Chung k\\u1ebft. K\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 ch\\u1ecdn 15 \\u0111\\u1ed9i s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 t\\u1eeb Ban T\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 9-5-2022.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">10 \\u0111\\u1ec1 l\\u1ecdt b\\u00e0o V\\u00f2ng Chung k\\u1ebft s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 28-5 \\u0111\\u1ebfn ng\\u00e0y 30-6-2022 tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi tham gia thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u \\u1edf V\\u00f2ng Chung k\\u1ebft.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">V\\u00f2ng Chung k\\u1ebft cu\\u1ed9c thi d\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 6-8-2022. T\\u1ea1i v\\u00f2ng chung k\\u1ebft, c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9i d\\u1ef1 thi c\\u00f3 t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a 07 ph\\u00fat tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y b\\u00e0i d\\u1ef1 thi v\\u00e0 Ban Gi\\u00e1m kh\\u1ea3o s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 10 ph\\u00fat \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1eb7t c\\u00e2u h\\u1ecfi.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">C\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i tham d\\u1ef1 cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 theo 6 ti\\u00eau ch\\u00ed: (1) T\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t c\\u1ee7a s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m\\/d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 c\\u00f3 \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a k\\u1ef9 thu\\u1eadt, c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7; (2) T\\u00ednh kh\\u1ea3 thi trong vi\\u1ec7c s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh; T\\u1ed1c \\u0111\\u1ed9 tri\\u1ec3n khai \\u0111\\u01b0a s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m\\/d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 ra th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng; (3) \\u0110\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 m\\u00f4 t\\u1ea3 v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3, c\\u00f3 s\\u1ed1 li\\u1ec7u kh\\u1ea3o s\\u00e1t; (4) \\u0110\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i m\\u00f4 t\\u1ea3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c k\\u00eanh ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u1edbi kh\\u00e1ch h\\u00e0ng; Gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o v\\u00e0 kh\\u00e1c bi\\u1ec7t; (5) T\\u00ednh \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf c\\u1ee7a s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m\\/d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 nh\\u1eb1m gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft v\\u1ea5n \\u0111\\u1ec1 mang t\\u00ednh th\\u1eed th\\u00e1ch c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i; (6) T\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c th\\u00e0nh vi\\u00ean gi\\u1ea3i th\\u00edch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c vai tr\\u00f2 v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3p trong \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n \\u0111ang theo h\\u1ecdc ho\\u1eb7c d\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ecbnh.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">B\\u00e0i d\\u1ef1 thi n\\u1ed9p tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ea1i V\\u0103n ph\\u00f2ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n Thanh ni\\u00ean - H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0110H\\u0110N (41 L\\u00ea Du\\u1ea9n, qu\\u1eadn H\\u1ea3i Ch\\u00e2u) tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc 17h00 ng\\u00e0y 3-4-2022. N\\u1ebfu n\\u1ed9p b\\u00e0i thi qua h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c chuy\\u1ec3n ph\\u00e1t nhanh\\/b\\u01b0u \\u0111i\\u1ec7n th\\u00ec c\\u1ea7n ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng thu x\\u1ebfp l\\u1ecbch g\\u1eedi \\u0111\\u1ec3 Ban T\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b\\u00e0i thi tr\\u1ec5 nh\\u1ea5t l\\u00e0 ng\\u00e0y 3-4-2022.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">\\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u1ef1 thi c\\u1ea7n n\\u1ed9p file m\\u1ec1m b\\u00e0i thi \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 email: <a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 122, 183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"mailto:inte.ud@gmail.com\\\">inte.ud@gmail.com<\\/a> v\\u1edbi ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u1ec1 ghi r\\u00f5 \\u201c[T\\u00caN NH\\u00d3M] D\\u1ef1 thi Cu\\u1ed9c thi KNCN trong SV l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 2\\u201d tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u00e0y 3-4-2022.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u201cKh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p C\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 trong sinh vi\\u00ean nh\\u1eb1m ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea1o c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m\\/d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5\\u2026 c\\u00f3 t\\u00ednh m\\u1edbi, t\\u00ednh \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0 kh\\u1ea3 thi nh\\u1eb1m ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea1o doanh nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c s\\u00e1ng l\\u1eadp kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng cho h\\u1ec7 sinh th\\u00e1i kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1ea1i \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng v\\u00e0 Mi\\u1ec1n Trung \\u2013 T\\u00e2y Nguy\\u00ean. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c, k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i gi\\u1eefa doanh nghi\\u1ec7p v\\u00e0 nh\\u00e0 tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng trong n\\u00e2ng cao ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o sinh vi\\u00ean - ngu\\u1ed3n nh\\u00e2n l\\u1ef1c ngh\\u1ec1 nghi\\u1ec7p\\/kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; Th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean n\\u1eafm \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c y\\u00eau c\\u1ea7u v\\u00e0 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh s\\u00e1ng l\\u1eadp\\/nh\\u00e2n l\\u1ef1c trong doanh nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, hi\\u1ec3u v\\u00e0 thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00e2m th\\u1ebf chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i sang t\\u01b0 duy t\\u00edch c\\u1ef1c, ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng trong c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c v\\u00e0 ngh\\u1ec1 nghi\\u1ec7p; H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t gi\\u1ea3i cho c\\u00e1c v\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m, doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ec3 ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n; Cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o t\\u00ednh thi\\u1ebft th\\u1ef1c, \\u00fd ngh\\u0129a, n\\u1ed9i dung s\\u00e2u s\\u1eafc, t\\u1ea1o th\\u00e0nh cu\\u1ed9c thi th\\u01b0\\u1eddng ni\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0110\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 10px;orphans:2