happy.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/03\\/bot-dong-trung-ha-thao-cordyhappy-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\\/\\/cordyhappy.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/03\\/bot-dong-trung-ha-thao-cordyhappy-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\\/\\/cordyhappy.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/03\\/bot-dong-trung-ha-thao-cordyhappy-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\\/\\/cordyhappy.vn\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2020\\/03\\/bot-dong-trung-ha-thao-cordyhappy-100x100.jpg 100w\\\" sizes=\\\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\\\" width=\\\"1200\\\" height=\\\"1200\\\"><\\/p><figure><figcaption class=\\\"wp-caption-text\\\" id=\\\"caption-attachment-4213\\\"><i>B\\u1ed9t \\u0110\\u00f4ng tr\\u00f9ng H\\u1ea1 th\\u1ea3o CordyHappy<\\/i><\\/figcaption><\\/figure><h3 style=\\\"margin-left:0px;\\\">C\\u00f4ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9t \\u0110\\u00f4ng tr\\u00f9ng H\\u1ea1 th\\u1ea3o<\\/h3><ul><li>B\\u1ed3i b\\u1ed5 c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3<\\/li><li>T\\u0103ng s\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u1ec1 kh\\u00e1ng<\\/li><li>H\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1eeba b\\u1ec7nh<\\/li><\\/ul><h3 style=\\\"margin-left:0px;\\\">H\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng B\\u1ed9t \\u0110\\u00f4ng tr\\u00f9ng H\\u1ea1 th\\u1ea3o<\\/h3><ul><li><strong>\\u0102n ch\\u00e1o:<\\/strong> M\\u00fac ch\\u00e1o ra b\\u00e1t, \\u0111\\u1ee3i kho\\u1ea3ng 5 ph\\u00fat cho nhi\\u1ec7t \\u0111\\u1ed9 c\\u1ee7a ch\\u00e1o h\\u1ea1 xu\\u1ed1ng kho\\u1ea3ng 70 \\u0111\\u1ed9 C. Cho 1 gram b\\u1ed9t \\u0110\\u00f4ng tr\\u00f9ng H\\u1ea1 th\\u1ea3o (kho\\u1ea3ng 1 th\\u00eca cafe nh\\u1ecf) v\\u00e0o, khu\\u1ea5y \\u0111\\u1ec1u v\\u00e0 th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c.<\\/li><li><strong>Ng\\u00e2m m\\u1eadt ong:&nbsp;<\\/strong><ul><li><em><i>Chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb:<\\/i><\\/em> Cho 10 gram b\\u1ed9t \\u0110\\u00f4ng tr\\u00f9ng H\\u1ea1 th\\u1ea3o v\\u00e0o 500 mL m\\u1eadt ong, khu\\u1ea5y \\u0111\\u1ec1u v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ec3 kho\\u1ea3ng 1 tu\\u1ea7n.<\\/li><li><em><i>S\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng:<\\/i><\\/em> L\\u1ea5y 1 th\\u00eca M\\u1eadt ong \\u0110\