(346, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\",\"slug\":\"hoat-dong-ho-tro-sinh-vien-khoi-nghiep\",\"slug_id\":\"84\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"V\\u1edbi m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u01b0a c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn g\\u1ea7n h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 truy\\u1ec1n ngu\\u1ed3n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng l\\u1edbn, t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 19-4, V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng (DNES) tri\\u1ec3n khai ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd cho ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cB\\u1ec7 ph\\u00f3ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d d\\u00e0nh cho \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean n\\u0103m 2022. Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh do Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p DNES t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 23, 24-4-2022.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tham gia l\\u00e0 t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 sinh vi\\u00ean y\\u00eau th\\u00edch kinh doanh, kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111ang theo h\\u1ecdc t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh g\\u1ed3m 2 giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n: Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 1 l\\u00e0 Bootcamp (kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng) \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c trong 2 ng\\u00e0y 23 v\\u00e0 24-4 v\\u1edbi 50 \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean. Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; X\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec3u v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; Hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00e2n dung c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng; Ki\\u1ec3m ch\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u1ea3 thi.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><a class=\\\"dng-img-viewer\\\" style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/21-4%20VUON%20UOM.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized\\\" style=\\\"width:695px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/21-4%20VUON%20UOM.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"><\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2 l\\u00e0 Incubator (\\u01b0\\u01a1m t\\u1ea1o) g\\u1ed3m 3 c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n ho\\u1eb7c nh\\u00f3m xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qua giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 1. C\\u00e1c c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n ho\\u1eb7c nh\\u00f3m s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u d\\u01b0\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n 1 k\\u00e8m 1 c\\u1ee7a chuy\\u00ean gia \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i s\\u00e2u v\\u00e0o x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng m\\u00f4 h\\u00ecnh kinh doanh kh\\u1ea3 thi. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, 3 c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n\\/nh\\u00f3m xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i tham gia chuy\\u1ebfn tham quan StartUp Tour; tham quan tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh v\\u00e0 giao l\\u01b0u tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c StartUp tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u00f4; Chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 tham gia v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c cu\\u1ed9c thi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p. \\u0110\\u0103ng k\\u00fd tham gia t\\u1ea1i link:&nbsp;<a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/forms.gle\\/iNfvWnZZaTrm62L47\\\">https:\\/\\/forms.gle\\/iNfvWnZZaTrm62L47<\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh DNES, Trung t\\u00e2m \\u01b0\\u01a1m t\\u1ea1o Kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p S\\u00f4ng H\\u00e0n (Songhan incubator) c\\u0169ng v\\u1eeba ra m\\u1eaft ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh Songhan incubator - Startup Internship Program (SHi \\u2013 SIP 2022). Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf v\\u1edbi l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o. C\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i startup v\\u00e0 sinh vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp b\\u1edfi c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n. \\u0110\\u0103ng k\\u00fd tham gia t\\u1ea1i <a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/forms.office.com\\/r\\/9PfjV8Fpgi\\\">https:\\/\\/forms.office.com\\/r\\/9PfjV8Fpgi.<\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:right;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>NGUY\\u00caN TH\\u1ea2O - https:\\/\\/danang.gov.vn\\/<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"4\",\"6\"],\"image\":\"news\\/7-1.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep sang tao\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"sinh vien\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"sinh vien khoi nghiep\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/100.0.4896.127 Safari/537.36', '42.115.174.66', 1, 2, 'Nhiều hoạt động hỗ trợ sinh viên khởi nghiệp', 'primary', '2022-05-10 21:01:48', '2022-05-10 21:01:48'),
(347, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"T\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm top 10 sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh 2022\",\"slug\":\"tim-kiem-top10-sinh-vien-khoi-nghiep-cong-nghe-tai-chinh-2022\",\"slug_id\":\"88\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"Cu\\u1ed9c thi cam k\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u00f9ng top 10 c\\u1ee7a cu\\u1ed9c thi Sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh Finnovation 2022, g\\u1ecdi v\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 kh\\u1edfi ngu\\u1ed3n \\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t 1.000 USD\\/d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"http:\\/\\/startup.kiendaotac.com\\/storage\\/news\\/3tt.png\\\" alt=\\\"3tt\\\"><\\/figure><p style=\\\"text-align:center;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:hsl(0,0%,100%);color:rgb(34,34,34);\\\"><i><span>Kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng cu\\u1ed9c thi Sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh 2022 - \\u1ea2nh: H\\u1ea2I \\u0110\\u0102NG&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Chi\\u1ec1u 18-4 t\\u1ea1i H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i di\\u1ec5n ra l\\u1ec5 ph\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng cu\\u1ed9c thi Sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh Finnovation 2022.<\\/p><p>Tham d\\u1ef1 l\\u1ec5 ph\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u00f3 Th\\u1ee9 tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng B\\u1ed9 Khoa h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 L\\u00ea Xu\\u00e2n \\u0110\\u1ecbnh; B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, Ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft.<\\/p><p>\\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 cu\\u1ed9c thi c\\u1ea5p qu\\u1ed1c gia \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean v\\u00e0 l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ea1o b\\u1edfi B\\u1ed9 Khoa h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7, Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n v\\u00e0 s\\u1ef1 tham gia c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb.<\\/p><p>Cu\\u1ed9c thi nh\\u1eb1m ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn, n\\u00e2ng cao nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ee9c c\\u1ee7a x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o v\\u00e0 s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7 trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh v\\u00e0 chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1, g\\u00f3p ph\\u1ea7n th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y h\\u1ec7 sinh th\\u00e1i kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n cho nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kinh doanh \\u0111\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u00e1o x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc l\\u1edbn m\\u1ea1nh v\\u00e0 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng ra qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf.<\\/p><p>Ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u t\\u1ea1i l\\u1ec5 ph\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft chia s\\u1ebb cu\\u1ed9c thi s\\u1ebd l\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i ch\\u1eafp c\\u00e1nh cho nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng, \\u01b0\\u1edbc m\\u01a1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7u n\\u1ed1i gi\\u1eefa thanh ni\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 doanh nh\\u00e2n th\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi kinh nghi\\u1ec7m th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng, t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i \\u0111\\u1ec3 bi\\u1ebfn \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh th\\u00e0nh hi\\u1ec7n th\\u1ef1c.<\\/p><div><div>&nbsp;<\\/div><\\/div><p>Cu\\u1ed9c thi s\\u1ebd di\\u1ec5n ra t\\u1eeb nay \\u0111\\u1ebfn ng\\u00e0y 12-8 k\\u1ebft h\\u1ee3p c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn.<\\/p><p>M\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau c\\u1ee7a Finnovation 2022 l\\u00e0 tuy\\u1ec3n ch\\u1ecdn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t 100 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0o v\\u00f2ng 1, 30 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n v\\u00e0o v\\u00f2ng 2 v\\u00e0 10 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n v\\u00e0o v\\u00f2ng chung k\\u1ebft.<\\/p><p>Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi \\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t 5 v\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m v\\u1ec1 fintech, proptech, \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o v\\u00e0 chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 trong v\\u00e0 ngo\\u00e0i n\\u01b0\\u1edbc; cam k\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u00f9ng top 10 c\\u1ee7a cu\\u1ed9c thi Finnovation, g\\u1ecdi v\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 kh\\u1edfi ngu\\u1ed3n \\u00edt nh\\u1ea5t 1.000 USD\\/d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n v\\u00e0 1 ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u cho m\\u1ed7i \\u0111\\u1ed9i v\\u00e0o chung k\\u1ebft, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng website\\/landing page v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed9 nh\\u1eadn di\\u1ec7n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u cho top 10 v\\u00e0o chung k\\u1ebft.<\\/p><p>Ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c cho bi\\u1ebft, s\\u1ebd c\\u00f3 1 gi\\u1ea3i nh\\u1ea5t, 2 gi\\u1ea3i nh\\u00ec, 2 gi\\u1ea3i ba. Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, gi\\u1ea3i nh\\u1ea5t s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u1eadn b\\u1eb1ng khen c\\u1ee7a Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, ti\\u1ec1n m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1ecb gi\\u00e1 50 tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, qu\\u00e0 t\\u1eb7ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng 50 tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u1ed3ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:right;\\\"><i><strong>Theo tuoitre.vn.<\\/strong><\\/i><\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"4\",\"6\"],\"image\":\"news\\/3-2.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"cong nghe\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"tai chinh\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"cuoc thi\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"2022\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/100.0.4896.127 Safari/537.36', '42.115.174.66', 1, 6, 'Tìm kiếm top 10 sinh viên khởi nghiệp công nghệ tài chính 2022', 'primary', '2022-05-10 21:02:16', '2022-05-10 21:02:16');
