tuy\\u00ean truy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c quan t\\u00e2m th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1eeb c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng n\\u1ed9i dung \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn l\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n...<\\/p><p>C\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ph\\u00e1t huy \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a vai tr\\u00f2 xung k\\u00edch, t\\u00ecnh nguy\\u1ec7n, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a thanh ni\\u00ean trong tham gia th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh, ph\\u1ea7n vi\\u1ec7c g\\u1eafn v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 ch\\u00ednh tr\\u1ecb, nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n t\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng...<\\/p><p>Li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u00f9ng thanh ni\\u00ean trong kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p, h\\u1ed9i nh\\u1eadp qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf; ch\\u0103m lo, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 thanh thi\\u1ebfu nhi: Ban th\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ee5 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c L\\u1ec5 h\\u1ed9i thanh ni\\u00ean (Youth Fest) v\\u1edbi th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p \\\"Th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi - Th\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng - K\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 Chia s\\u1ebb\\\" thu h\\u00fat h\\u01a1n 25.000 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, thanh ni\\u00ean tham gia v\\u00e0 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u00e1c tr\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1ea1ng.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Ban th\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ee5 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM \\u0111\\u00e3 ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi b\\u00e1o <i>Tu\\u1ed5i Tr\\u1ebb<\\/i> trao t\\u1eb7ng 2.000 su\\u1ea5t h\\u1ecdc b\\u1ed5ng cho t\\u00e2n sinh vi\\u00ean, h\\u1ecdc sinh v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng kinh ph\\u00ed h\\u01a1n 18 t\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng; ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi H\\u1ed9i LHTN VN TP t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c gi\\u1ea3i \\\"Tu\\u1ed5i Tr\\u1ebb Golf Tournament for Start-up 2022\\\", t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 trao h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 cho 30 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o tr\\u1ebb...<\\/p><div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\\\"><div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/mg0778-1650626148187238865575.jpg\\\" title=\\\"Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft, b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, trao b\\u1eb1ng khen cho c\\u00e1c t\\u1eadp th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch cao trong chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized lightbox-content\\\" style=\\\"width:586px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/thumb_w\\/586\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/mg0778-1650626148187238865575.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 2.\\\" title=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 2.\\\"><\\/a><\\/div><div class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption ck_legend caption\\\"><p>Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft, b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, trao b\\u1eb1ng khen cho c\\u00e1c t\\u1eadp th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch cao trong chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><p>V\\u1ec1 nh\\u1eefng h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf, ch\\u1ecb H\\u00e0 cho r\\u1eb1ng vi\\u1ec7c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean \\\"Tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o\\\" v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh v\\u1eabn ch\\u01b0a c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n. T\\u00ednh d\\u1ef1 b\\u00e1o trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau trong Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean ch\\u01b0a cao, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t xa nh\\u01b0ng c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau ch\\u01b0a ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh.<\\/p><p>Vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec3m m\\u1edbi cho c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng mang t\\u00ednh truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1edbi t\\u1ea1i c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf ch\\u01b0a r\\u00f5 n\\u00e9t. T\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 m\\u00e0 quy m\\u00f4, s\\u1ee9c h\\u00fat c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ea1t nh\\u01b0 mong mu\\u1ed1n...<\\/p><div><div>&nbsp;<\\/div><\\/div><p>\\\"Tuy d\\u1ecbch b\\u1ec7nh \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t t\\u1ed1t nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn c\\u00f2n di\\u1ec5n bi\\u1ebfn ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c bi\\u1ebfn ch\\u1ee7ng m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1i \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ebfn ti\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9, quy m\\u00f4, vi\\u1ec7c v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea7n kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n...\\\", ch\\u1ecb H\\u00e0 n\\u00eau.<\\/p><div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\\\"><div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0765-1650625464726492485531.jpg\\\" title=\\\"Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized lightbox-content\\\" style=\\\"width:586px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/thumb_w\\/586\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0765-1650625464726492485531.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 3.\\\" title=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 3.\\\"><\\/a><\\/div><div class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption ck_legend caption\\\"><p>Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><p>Ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ea1o t\\u1ea1i h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb, anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam - b\\u00e0y t\\u1ecf s\\u1ef1 nh\\u1ea5t tr\\u00ed v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng tin c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb. T\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y, anh Tri\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng chia s\\u1ebb, \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao nh\\u1eefng k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 m\\u00e0 tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb TP.HCM \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c qua chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean l\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0y.<\\/p><p>\\\"Qua l\\u1ea7n d\\u1ef1 h\\u00f4m ra qu\\u00e2n ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u l\\u1eabn h\\u00f4m nay, t\\u00f4i c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn r\\u00f5 quy\\u1ebft t\\u00e2m th\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed7 l\\u1ef1c h\\u1ebft m\\u00ecnh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi chu\\u1ed7i ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0y. R\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t b\\u1edfi v\\u00ec khi kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean ch\\u00fang ta ch\\u1ec9 v\\u1eeba quay l\\u1ea1i t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng b\\u00ecnh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng m\\u1edbi, m\\u1ecdi ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1eabn c\\u00f2n nhi\\u1ec1u r\\u00e0o c\\u1ea3n\\\", anh Tri\\u1ebft chia s\\u1ebb.<\\/p><p>Ch\\u1ecb Phan Th\\u1ecb Thanh Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM - ghi nh\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfp thu nh\\u1eefng chia s\\u1ebb, \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea5p c\\u00f9ng h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>\\\"Th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf ngay th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean th\\u00ec l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n ch\\u00fang ta c\\u00f3 qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u00e0 F0, th\\u1eadm ch\\u00ed c\\u00f3 anh ch\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u00e3 b\\u1ecb l\\u1ea7n 2, l\\u1ea7n 3. T\\u00ecnh th\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 v\\u1eabn k\\u00e9o d\\u00e0i cho t\\u1edbi chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u00e8 di\\u1ec5n ra, tuy nhi\\u00ean b\\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\\u1ec7m v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng g\\u00ec \\u0111\\u00e3 l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u00ec t\\u00f4i tin ch\\u00fang ta s\\u1ebd ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng\\\", ch\\u1ecb Thanh Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng chia s\\u1ebb.<\\/p><div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\\\"><div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0804-1650625469787941341777.jpg\\\" title=\\\"Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM khen th\\u01b0\\u1edfng m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb c\\u00f3 th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc trong Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized lightbox-content\\\" style=\\\"width:586px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/thumb_w\\/586\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0804-1650625469787941341777.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 4.\\\" title=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 4.\\\"><\\/a><\\/div><div class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption ck_legend caption\\\"><p>Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM khen th\\u01b0\\u1edfng m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb c\\u00f3 th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc trong Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:right;\\\"><i><strong>Theo tuoitre.vn.<\\/strong><\\/i><\\/p><\\/div><\\/div>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"4\",\"6\"],\"image\":\"news\\/mg0778-1650626148187238865575.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"thanh nien\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"lap nghiep\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/101.0.4951.54 Safari/537.36', '14.241.81.27', 1, 11, 'Sôi nổi Tháng thanh niên 2022 với nhiều hoạt động đồng hành khởi nghiệp, lập nghiệp', 'primary', '2022-05-17 00:34:23', '2022-05-17 00:34:23'),
(413, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Ph\\u00e1t huy t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a ngu\\u1ed3n nh\\u00e2n l\\u1ef1c, th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o\",\"slug\":\"thuc-day-manh-me-khoi-nghiep-sang-tao\",\"slug_id\":\"89\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"Ng\\u00e0y 26\\/3, t\\u1ea1i t\\u1ec9nh V\\u0129nh Ph\\u00fac, B\\u1ed9 Gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0 \\u0110\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o, Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n Thanh ni\\u00ean C\\u1ed9ng s\\u1ea3n H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh, UBND t\\u1ec9nh V\\u0129nh Ph\\u00fac v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb li\\u00ean quan ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i Kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p qu\\u1ed1c gia c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 IV (SV_STARTUP). Th\\u1ee7 t\\u01b0\\u1edbng Ch\\u00ednh ph\\u1ee7 Ph\\u1ea1m Minh Ch\\u00ednh d\\u1ef1 v\\u00e0 ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea1i Ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng ch\\u00ed Ph\\u1ea1m Minh Ch\\u00ednh kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh: \\u0110\\u1ea3ng, Nh\\u00e0 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc lu\\u00f4n quan t\\u00e2m \\u0111\\u1ebfn phong tr\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, c\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf, ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch, \\u0111\\u1ec1 \\u00e1n, t\\u1ea1o m\\u1ecdi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i cho kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p. \\u0110\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 K\\u1ebft lu\\u1eadn s\\u1ed1 14-KL\\/TW ng\\u00e0y 22\\/9\\/2021 c\\u1ee7a B\\u1ed9 Ch\\u00ednh tr\\u1ecb v\\u1ec1 ch\\u1ee7 tr\\u01b0\\u01a1ng khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch, b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 c\\u00e1n b\\u1ed9 n\\u0103ng \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o v\\u00ec l\\u1ee3i \\u00edch chung v\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c \\u0110\\u1ec1 \\u00e1n 844, 939, 1665 c\\u1ee7a Ch\\u00ednh ph\\u1ee7 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 h\\u1ec7 sinh th\\u00e1i kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p qu\\u1ed1c gia, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef, sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/skhcn.bacgiang.gov.vn\\/documents\\/21435\\/13855330\\/1649045155666_63.2.jpeg\\/e7561a53-3b4e-4c5e-b3c3-a2f41f84040d?t=1649045155669\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"313\\\" width=\\\"500\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><em><i><span>Th\\u1ee7 t\\u01b0\\u1edbng Ph\\u1ea1m Minh Ch\\u00ednh ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn t\\u1ea1i bu\\u1ed5i l\\u1ec5&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>91 n\\u0103m qua, \\u0110o\\u00e0n Thanh ni\\u00ean C\\u1ed9ng s\\u1ea3n H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh \\u0111\\u00e3 l\\u00e0m t\\u1ed1t nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 \\u0111o\\u00e0n k\\u1ebft, t\\u1eadp h\\u1ee3p, gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c, v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng thanh ni\\u00ean tham gia c\\u00f4ng vi\\u1ec7c chung c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u1edbi tinh th\\u1ea7n \\u201c\\u0110\\u00e2u c\\u1ea7n thanh ni\\u00ean c\\u00f3, vi\\u1ec7c g\\u00ec kh\\u00f3 thanh ni\\u00ean l\\u00e0m\\u201d.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Trong c\\u00f4ng cu\\u1ed9c \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed9i nh\\u1eadp qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf, tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb c\\u1ea3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc \\u0111\\u00e3 ph\\u00e1t huy truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng qu\\u00fd b\\u00e1u c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 cha anh, s\\u1edbm th\\u00edch nghi v\\u1edbi \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ki\\u1ec7n m\\u1edbi, c\\u00f3 \\u00fd ch\\u00ed v\\u01b0\\u01a1n l\\u00ean l\\u1eadp th\\u00e2n, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p, ti\\u00ean phong, xung k\\u00edch, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, d\\u1ea5n th\\u00e2n, lu\\u00f4n c\\u00f3 m\\u1eb7t \\u1edf nh\\u1eefng n\\u01a1i kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n, gian kh\\u1ed5 v\\u00e0 s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u00f3n nh\\u1eadn nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 m\\u1edbi.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>\\u0110i\\u1ec3m l\\u1ea1i m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 trong V\\u0103n ki\\u1ec7n \\u0110\\u1ea1i h\\u1ed9i XIII c\\u1ee7a \\u0110\\u1ea3ng v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 qu\\u1ed1c gia, ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf s\\u1ed1 tr\\u00ean n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng khoa h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7, \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, kinh doanh, th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 nh\\u1eefng thu\\u1eadn l\\u1ee3i, c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n, th\\u00e1ch th\\u1ee9c \\u0111an xen, c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea7n nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n, Th\\u1ee7 t\\u01b0\\u1edbng Ph\\u1ea1m Minh Ch\\u00ednh nh\\u1ea5n m\\u1ea1nh: nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 c\\u1ee7a c\\u1ea3 h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng ch\\u00ednh tr\\u1ecb l\\u00e0 ph\\u1ea3i ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n, to\\u00e0n di\\u1ec7n gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o; x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng ngu\\u1ed3n nh\\u00e2n l\\u1ef1c m\\u1ea1nh c\\u1ea3 v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ed1 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng theo tinh th\\u1ea7n l\\u1ea5y t\\u00e0i n\\u0103ng, tr\\u00ed tu\\u1ec7, ph\\u1ea9m ch\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam l\\u00e0m trung t\\u00e2m, m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng l\\u1ef1c ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n quan tr\\u1ecdng nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ea5t n\\u01b0\\u1edbc.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, ph\\u1ea3i \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng v\\u1ec1 \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch t\\u01b0 duy \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, ph\\u00e1 v\\u1ee1 nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ki\\u1ebfn, r\\u00e0o c\\u1ea3n, l\\u1ed1i m\\u00f2n trong t\\u01b0 duy; th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd h\\u1ec7 sinh th\\u00e1i kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p ng\\u00e0nh gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c n\\u00f3i chung, trong c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng n\\u00f3i ri\\u00eang.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Nh\\u00e0 tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, c\\u00e1c th\\u1ea7y, c\\u00f4 gi\\u00e1o ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi truy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean x\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ecbnh r\\u00f5 m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00edch c\\u1ee7a vi\\u1ec7c h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp, c\\u00f3 tinh th\\u1ea7n h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp, thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i t\\u00e2m th\\u1ebf khi ra tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng; khuy\\u1ebfn kh\\u00edch sinh vi\\u00ean c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng s\\u00e1ng ki\\u1ebfn, \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, t\\u1ea1o ra nh\\u1eefng m\\u00f4 h\\u00ecnh kinh doanh m\\u1edbi, c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ec1 t\\u00e0i nghi\\u00ean c\\u1ee9u \\u1ee9ng d\\u1ee5ng c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i h\\u00f3a ho\\u1eb7c \\u00e1p d\\u1ee5ng v\\u00e0o th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf, h\\u00ecnh th\\u00e0nh c\\u00e1c doanh nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, t\\u1ea1o ra gi\\u00e1 tr\\u1ecb cho c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng v\\u00e0 cho to\\u00e0n x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Th\\u1ee7 t\\u01b0\\u1edbng Ph\\u1ea1m Minh Ch\\u00ednh l\\u01b0u \\u00fd: ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c ph\\u00e1t huy truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Vi\\u1ec7t Nam th\\u00f4ng minh, c\\u1ea7n c\\u00f9, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o, b\\u1ea3n l\\u0129nh, d\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ea7u v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n, th\\u1eed th\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ec3 th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o; ph\\u00e1t huy t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi, th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd tinh th\\u1ea7n kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o; \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o ng\\u00e0nh gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>\\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, t\\u1ea1o m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, thu h\\u00fat ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o; \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh h\\u1ee3p t\\u00e1c, m\\u1edf r\\u1ed9ng li\\u00ean k\\u1ebft, k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u00e0 qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf. C\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng c\\u1ea7n t\\u1eebng b\\u01b0\\u1edbc x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng c\\u01a1 ch\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u1eb7t h\\u00e0ng, giao nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 cho c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o nh\\u1eb1m th\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf-x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i theo h\\u01b0\\u1edbng xanh, b\\u1ec1n v\\u1eefng.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n c\\u1ea7n c\\u00f3 gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p t\\u1ea1o m\\u00f4i tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o; \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh vi\\u1ec7c th\\u00e0nh l\\u1eadp c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb chuy\\u00ean tr\\u00e1ch h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 thanh ni\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng gi\\u1ea3i ph\\u00e1p h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 t\\u00e0i n\\u0103ng tr\\u1ebb trong kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 \\u1edf v\\u00f9ng s\\u00e2u, v\\u00f9ng xa, \\u0111\\u1ed3ng b\\u00e0o d\\u00e2n t\\u1ed9c thi\\u1ec3u s\\u1ed1; t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng thu h\\u00fat ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c cho kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o; qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd, s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 Qu\\u1ef9 qu\\u1ed1c gia h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 Thanh ni\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/skhcn.bacgiang.gov.vn\\/documents\\/21435\\/13855330\\/1649045195359_63.4.jpeg\\/cb98f921-32e6-4e9c-970b-34b566c65a27?t=1649045195363\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"313\\\" width=\\\"500\\\"><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><em><i><span>Th\\u1ee7 t\\u01b0\\u1edbng Ph\\u1ea1m Minh Ch\\u00ednh tham quan c\\u00e1c gian h\\u00e0ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1ea1i Ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>N\\u0103m nay, Ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u00ednh: phi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ed1i tho\\u1ea1i ch\\u00ednh s\\u00e1ch \\u201cTh\\u00fac \\u0111\\u1ea9y ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n h\\u1ec7 sinh th\\u00e1i kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p cho h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean - Vai tr\\u00f2 c\\u1ee7a nh\\u00e0 tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, doanh nghi\\u1ec7p, qu\\u1ef9 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng\\u201d, Di\\u1ec5n \\u0111\\u00e0n \\u201cTruy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p cho h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean theo nh\\u00f3m ng\\u00e0nh\\u201d, chung k\\u1ebft Cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u201cH\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u1edbi&nbsp; \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 IV\\u201d.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, Cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u201cH\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u1edbi&nbsp;\\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 IV\\u201d l\\u00e0 \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n c\\u1ee7a Ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tri\\u1ec3n khai tr\\u00ean ph\\u1ea1m vi c\\u1ea3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 tham gia c\\u1ee7a 400 tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng, trung c\\u1ea5p, trung h\\u1ecdc c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf, trung h\\u1ecdc ph\\u1ed5 th\\u00f4ng. D\\u00e0nh cho h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean t\\u1eeb 12-24 tu\\u1ed5i, Cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ph\\u00e1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 4\\/2021, ghi nh\\u1eadn g\\u1ea7n 400 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n g\\u1eedi d\\u1ef1 thi. Trong \\u0111\\u00f3, 70 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n \\u0111\\u00e3 l\\u1ecdt v\\u00e0o chung k\\u1ebft.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,51,51);\\\"><span>T\\u1ea1i Ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i, \\u0111\\u00e1ng ch\\u00fa \\u00fd c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 kho\\u1ea3ng 140 gian tr\\u01b0ng b\\u00e0y \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\\u00ean v\\u00e0 1 s\\u1ed1 doanh nghi\\u1ec7p thu\\u1ed9c c\\u00e1c l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c khoa h\\u1ecdc, c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7; c\\u00f4ng nghi\\u1ec7p, ch\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m; n\\u00f4ng, l\\u00e2m, ng\\u01b0 nghi\\u1ec7p; gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c, y t\\u1ebf; d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5, du l\\u1ecbch; t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh, ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng; kinh doanh t\\u1ea1o t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i\\u2026&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:right;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;\\\"><span><strong style=\\\"color:rgb(0,97,212);\\\">Ngu\\u1ed3n: https:\\/\\/nhandan.vn\\/<\\/strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:200;line-height:15pt;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p><p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"6\"],\"image\":\"news\\/cd43a6c4-d3b9-4f81-bed1-280dcc9-1648290606433.jpeg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep sang tao\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"ngay hoi khoi nghiep\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/101.0.4951.54 Safari/537.36', '14.241.81.27', 1, 7, 'Phát huy tối đa nguồn nhân lực, thúc đẩy mạnh mẽ khởi nghiệp sáng tạo', 'primary', '2022-05-17 00:34:39', '2022-05-17 00:34:39'),
(414, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p\",\"slug\":\"hoat-dong-dong-hanh-khoi-nghiep-lap-nghiep\",\"slug_id\":\"93\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"Theo d\\u00f5i h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb t\\u1ed5ng k\\u1ebft Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 di\\u1ec5n ra v\\u00e0o chi\\u1ec1u 22-4 t\\u1ea1i Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM, nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, thanh ni\\u00ean b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc lo\\u1ea1t k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t trong vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u00f9ng thanh ni\\u00ean l\\u1eadp th\\u00e2n, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p.\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p><span>Ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u t\\u1ea1i h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb, ch\\u1ecb Tr\\u1ea7n Thu H\\u00e0 - ph\\u00f3 b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM - nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/tuoitre.vn\\/thang-thanh-nien.html\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"Th\\u00e1ng Thanh ni\\u00ean\\\"><span>Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean<\\/span> <\\/a><span>n\\u0103m 2022 c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ea1t.<\\/span> &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<\\/p><p>V\\u1ec1 nh\\u1eefng m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c, ch\\u1ecb H\\u00e0 cho r\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u00f3 l\\u00e0 vi\\u1ec7c c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea5p b\\u1ed9 \\u0110o\\u00e0n TP \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 s\\u1ef1 chuy\\u1ec3n bi\\u1ebfn linh ho\\u1ea1t trong thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u1ee9c tri\\u1ec3n khai c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi di\\u1ec5n bi\\u1ebfn m\\u1edbi nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a d\\u1ecbch b\\u1ec7nh COVID-19. C\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c tuy\\u00ean truy\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c quan t\\u00e2m th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1eeb c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng n\\u1ed9i dung \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u1ecdn l\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0 \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n...<\\/p><p>C\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ph\\u00e1t huy \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed1i \\u0111a vai tr\\u00f2 xung k\\u00edch, t\\u00ecnh nguy\\u1ec7n, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a thanh ni\\u00ean trong tham gia th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c c\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ecnh, ph\\u1ea7n vi\\u1ec7c g\\u1eafn v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 ch\\u00ednh tr\\u1ecb, nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n t\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng...<\\/p><p>Li\\u00ean quan \\u0111\\u1ebfn vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh c\\u00f9ng thanh ni\\u00ean trong kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p, h\\u1ed9i nh\\u1eadp qu\\u1ed1c t\\u1ebf; ch\\u0103m lo, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 thanh thi\\u1ebfu nhi: Ban th\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ee5 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c L\\u1ec5 h\\u1ed9i thanh ni\\u00ean (Youth Fest) v\\u1edbi th\\u00f4ng \\u0111i\\u1ec7p \\\"Th\\u1ebf h\\u1ec7 m\\u1edbi - Th\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng - K\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 Chia s\\u1ebb\\\" thu h\\u00fat h\\u01a1n 25.000 l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean, thanh ni\\u00ean tham gia v\\u00e0 t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u00e1c tr\\u00ean kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1ea1ng.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Ban th\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ee5 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM \\u0111\\u00e3 ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi b\\u00e1o <i>Tu\\u1ed5i Tr\\u1ebb<\\/i> trao t\\u1eb7ng 2.000 su\\u1ea5t h\\u1ecdc b\\u1ed5ng cho t\\u00e2n sinh vi\\u00ean, h\\u1ecdc sinh v\\u1edbi t\\u1ed5ng kinh ph\\u00ed h\\u01a1n 18 t\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng; ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi H\\u1ed9i LHTN VN TP t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c gi\\u1ea3i \\\"Tu\\u1ed5i Tr\\u1ebb Golf Tournament for Start-up 2022\\\", t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 trao h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 cho 30 d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o tr\\u1ebb...<\\/p><div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\\\"><div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/mg0778-1650626148187238865575.jpg\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft, b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, trao b\\u1eb1ng khen cho c\\u00e1c t\\u1eadp th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch cao trong chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized lightbox-content\\\" style=\\\"width:586px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/thumb_w\\/586\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/mg0778-1650626148187238865575.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 2.\\\" title=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 2.\\\"><\\/a><\\/div><div class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption ck_legend caption\\\"><p>Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft, b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, trao b\\u1eb1ng khen cho c\\u00e1c t\\u1eadp th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u1ea1t th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch cao trong chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><p>V\\u1ec1 nh\\u1eefng h\\u1ea1n ch\\u1ebf, ch\\u1ecb H\\u00e0 cho r\\u1eb1ng vi\\u1ec7c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean \\\"Tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o\\\" v\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh v\\u1eabn ch\\u01b0a c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111i\\u1ec3m nh\\u1ea5n. T\\u00ednh d\\u1ef1 b\\u00e1o trong vi\\u1ec7c x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng h\\u1ec7 th\\u1ed1ng ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau trong Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean ch\\u01b0a cao, t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t xa nh\\u01b0ng c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9 ti\\u00eau ch\\u01b0a ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh.<\\/p><p>Vi\\u1ec7c \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u01b0, t\\u1ea1o \\u0111i\\u1ec3m m\\u1edbi cho c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng mang t\\u00ednh truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng, thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf c\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng m\\u1edbi t\\u1ea1i c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf ch\\u01b0a r\\u00f5 n\\u00e9t. T\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00f3 m\\u00e0 quy m\\u00f4, s\\u1ee9c h\\u00fat c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh v\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ea1t nh\\u01b0 mong mu\\u1ed1n...<\\/p><div><div>&nbsp;<\\/div><\\/div><p>\\\"Tuy d\\u1ecbch b\\u1ec7nh \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ec3m so\\u00e1t t\\u1ed1t nh\\u01b0ng v\\u1eabn c\\u00f2n di\\u1ec5n bi\\u1ebfn ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c bi\\u1ebfn ch\\u1ee7ng m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea1i \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ebfn ti\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9, quy m\\u00f4, vi\\u1ec7c v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng c\\u00e1c ngu\\u1ed3n l\\u1ef1c x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i c\\u00f3 ph\\u1ea7n kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n...\\\", ch\\u1ecb H\\u00e0 n\\u00eau.<\\/p><div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\\\"><div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0765-1650625464726492485531.jpg\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized lightbox-content\\\" style=\\\"width:586px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/thumb_w\\/586\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0765-1650625464726492485531.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 3.\\\" title=\\\"S\\u00f4i n\\u1ed5i Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p - \\u1ea2nh 3.\\\"><\\/a><\\/div><div class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption ck_legend caption\\\"><p>Anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><p>Ph\\u00e1t bi\\u1ec3u ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ea1o t\\u1ea1i h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb, anh Nguy\\u1ec5n Minh Tri\\u1ebft - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Ban ch\\u1ea5p h\\u00e0nh Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch Trung \\u01b0\\u01a1ng H\\u1ed9i Sinh vi\\u00ean Vi\\u1ec7t Nam - b\\u00e0y t\\u1ecf s\\u1ef1 nh\\u1ea5t tr\\u00ed v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng tin c\\u1ee7a h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb. T\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u00e2y, anh Tri\\u1ebft c\\u0169ng chia s\\u1ebb, \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 cao nh\\u1eefng k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 m\\u00e0 tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb TP.HCM \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c qua chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean l\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0y.<\\/p><p>\\\"Qua l\\u1ea7n d\\u1ef1 h\\u00f4m ra qu\\u00e2n ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u l\\u1eabn h\\u00f4m nay, t\\u00f4i c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadn r\\u00f5 quy\\u1ebft t\\u00e2m th\\u00edch \\u1ee9ng v\\u00e0 n\\u1ed7 l\\u1ef1c h\\u1ebft m\\u00ecnh c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi chu\\u1ed7i ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u1ea7n n\\u00e0y. R\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t b\\u1edfi v\\u00ec khi kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean ch\\u00fang ta ch\\u1ec9 v\\u1eeba quay l\\u1ea1i t\\u00ecnh tr\\u1ea1ng b\\u00ecnh th\\u01b0\\u1eddng m\\u1edbi, m\\u1ecdi ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1eabn c\\u00f2n nhi\\u1ec1u r\\u00e0o c\\u1ea3n\\\", anh Tri\\u1ebft chia s\\u1ebb.<\\/p><p>Ch\\u1ecb Phan Th\\u1ecb Thanh Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng - b\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM - ghi nh\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 ti\\u1ebfp thu nh\\u1eefng chia s\\u1ebb, \\u00fd ki\\u1ebfn c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea5p c\\u00f9ng h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>\\\"Th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf ngay th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean th\\u00ec l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0110o\\u00e0n ch\\u00fang ta c\\u00f3 qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi l\\u00e0 F0, th\\u1eadm ch\\u00ed c\\u00f3 anh ch\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u00e3 b\\u1ecb l\\u1ea7n 2, l\\u1ea7n 3. T\\u00ecnh th\\u1ebf \\u0111\\u00f3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 v\\u1eabn k\\u00e9o d\\u00e0i cho t\\u1edbi chu\\u1ed7i ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u00e8 di\\u1ec5n ra, tuy nhi\\u00ean b\\u1eb1ng kinh nghi\\u1ec7m v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng g\\u00ec \\u0111\\u00e3 l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u00ec t\\u00f4i tin ch\\u00fang ta s\\u1ebd ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c chi\\u1ebfn th\\u1eafng\\\", ch\\u1ecb Thanh Ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng chia s\\u1ebb.<\\/p><div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode active\\\"><div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.tuoitre.vn\\/2022\\/4\\/22\\/logo-mg0804-1650625469787941341777.jpg\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"Th\\u00e0nh \\u0111o\\u00e0n TP.HCM khen th\\u01b0\\u1edfng m\\u1ed9t s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01a1n v\\u1ecb c\\u00f3 th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc trong Th\\u00e1ng thanh ni\\u00ean 2022 - \\u1ea2nh: C\\u00d4NG TRI\\u1ec6U\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized lightbox-content\