(418, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Kh\\u01a1i d\\u1eady, ti\\u1ebfp s\\u1ee9c nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p trong \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean\",\"slug\":\"khoi-day-tiep-suc-nhung-y-tuong-khoi-nghiep-trong-doan-vien-thanh-nien\",\"slug_id\":\"130\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"Ng\\u00e0y 23-4, Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 (DNES) t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c kh\\u00f3a t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n Bootcamp v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p cho \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean l\\u00e0 sinh vi\\u00ean c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n di\\u1ec5n ra trong 2 ng\\u00e0y, 23 v\\u00e0 24-4 v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><a class=\\\"dng-img-viewer\\\" style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP%203.JPG\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized\\\" style=\\\"width:695px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP%203.JPG\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"><\\/a><br><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0,0,255);\\\"><em><i><span>Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a DNES&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n xoay quanh c\\u00e1c n\\u1ed9i dung: T\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u 2 k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng quan tr\\u1ecdng c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai, ph\\u00e2n nh\\u00f3m \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u00ean \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng; Th\\u1ef1c h\\u00e0nh qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00ean \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng, ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n; Tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kinh doanh. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, ch\\u00e2n dung nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng, th\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec3u nh\\u1eefng&nbsp;kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n m\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c startup g\\u1eb7p ph\\u1ea3i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ph\\u00f3 B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n L\\u00ea C\\u00f4ng H\\u00f9ng cho bi\\u1ebft, ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh nh\\u1eb1m h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn, hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 nh\\u1eefng ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0 k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">\\u201cTh\\u00f4ng qua ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i mong mu\\u1ed1n c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ebb c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi \\u0111\\u1ec3 v\\u1eadn d\\u1ee5ng linh ho\\u1ea1t ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u00e3 h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0o th\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ec5n; \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi kh\\u01a1i d\\u1eady nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 gi\\u00fap c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch tri\\u1ec3n khai \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u00f3 trong t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai g\\u1ea7n\\u201d, anh H\\u00f9ng n\\u00f3i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><a class=\\\"dng-img-viewer\\\" style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized\\\" style=\\\"width:695px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"><\\/a><br><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0,0,255);\\\"><em><i><span>C\\u00e1c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u01b0a ra t\\u1ea1i bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n g\\u00f3p \\u00fd, ph\\u1ea3n bi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh theo h\\u01b0\\u1edbng kh\\u1ea3 thi&nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">C\\u00e1c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u01b0a ra t\\u1ea1i bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n g\\u00f3p \\u00fd, ph\\u1ea3n bi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p. Top 3 \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n, tham gia c\\u00e1c cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u1edf \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng v\\u00e0 \\u01b0\\u01a1m t\\u1ea1o giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:right;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>NGUY\\u00caN TH\\u1ea2O - https:\\/\\/danang.gov.vn\\/<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"6\"],\"image\":\"news\\/23-4-td-khoi-nghiep.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep sang tao\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"y tuong khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"doan vien\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"thanh nien\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/101.0.4951.54 Safari/537.36', '14.241.81.27', 1, 12, 'Khơi dậy, tiếp sức những ý tưởng khởi nghiệp trong đoàn viên thanh niên', 'primary', '2022-05-17 00:35:42', '2022-05-17 00:35:42');
