(432, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Kh\\u01a1i d\\u1eady, ti\\u1ebfp s\\u1ee9c nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p trong \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean\",\"slug\":\"khoi-day-tiep-suc-nhung-y-tuong-khoi-nghiep-trong-doan-vien-thanh-nien\",\"slug_id\":\"130\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"Ng\\u00e0y 23-4, Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p v\\u1edbi V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 (DNES) t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c kh\\u00f3a t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n Bootcamp v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p cho \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean l\\u00e0 sinh vi\\u00ean c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n di\\u1ec5n ra trong 2 ng\\u00e0y, 23 v\\u00e0 24-4 v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><a class=\\\"dng-img-viewer\\\" style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP%203.JPG\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized\\\" style=\\\"width:695px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP%203.JPG\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"><\\/a><br><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0,0,255);\\\"><em><i><span>Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ph\\u1ed1i v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u1ee7a DNES&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n xoay quanh c\\u00e1c n\\u1ed9i dung: T\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u 2 k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng quan tr\\u1ecdng c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai, ph\\u00e2n nh\\u00f3m \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u00ean \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng; Th\\u1ef1c h\\u00e0nh qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00ean \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng, ph\\u00e2n t\\u00edch th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng, xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n; Tr\\u00ecnh b\\u00e0y \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kinh doanh. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, ch\\u00e2n dung nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng, th\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec3u nh\\u1eefng&nbsp;kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n m\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c startup g\\u1eb7p ph\\u1ea3i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ph\\u00f3 B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n L\\u00ea C\\u00f4ng H\\u00f9ng cho bi\\u1ebft, ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh nh\\u1eb1m h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean thanh ni\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn, hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 nh\\u1eefng ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0 k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">\\u201cTh\\u00f4ng qua ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh, ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i mong mu\\u1ed1n c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n tr\\u1ebb c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ecfi \\u0111\\u1ec3 v\\u1eadn d\\u1ee5ng linh ho\\u1ea1t ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c \\u0111\\u00e3 h\\u1ecdc v\\u00e0o th\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ec5n; \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi kh\\u01a1i d\\u1eady nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 gi\\u00fap c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch tri\\u1ec3n khai \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng \\u0111\\u00f3 trong t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai g\\u1ea7n\\u201d, anh H\\u00f9ng n\\u00f3i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:center;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><a class=\\\"dng-img-viewer\\\" style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized\\\" style=\\\"width:695px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/23-4%20TD-KHOI%20NGHIEP.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"><\\/a><br><span style=\\\"color:rgb(0,0,255);\\\"><em><i><span>C\\u00e1c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u01b0a ra t\\u1ea1i bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n g\\u00f3p \\u00fd, ph\\u1ea3n bi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh theo h\\u01b0\\u1edbng kh\\u1ea3 thi&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/i><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">C\\u00e1c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0111\\u01b0a ra t\\u1ea1i bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n g\\u00f3p \\u00fd, ph\\u1ea3n bi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ec9nh ph\\u00f9 h\\u1ee3p. Top 3 \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 \\u0111\\u1ec3 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n, tham gia c\\u00e1c cu\\u1ed9c thi \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p \\u1edf \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng v\\u00e0 \\u01b0\\u01a1m t\\u1ea1o giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:right;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>NGUY\\u00caN TH\\u1ea2O - https:\\/\\/danang.gov.vn\\/<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"8\"],\"image\":\"news\\/23-4-td-khoi-nghiep.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep sang tao\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"y tuong khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"doan vien\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"thanh nien\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/101.0.4951.54 Safari/537.36', '14.241.81.27', 1, 12, 'Khơi dậy, tiếp sức những ý tưởng khởi nghiệp trong đoàn viên thanh niên', 'primary', '2022-05-17 00:49:14', '2022-05-17 00:49:14'),
(433, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Nhi\\u1ec1u ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 sinh vi\\u00ean kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\",\"slug\":\"hoat-dong-ho-tro-sinh-vien-khoi-nghiep\",\"slug_id\":\"84\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"V\\u1edbi m\\u1ee5c ti\\u00eau \\u0111\\u01b0a c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn g\\u1ea7n h\\u01a1n v\\u1edbi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p c\\u0169ng nh\\u01b0 truy\\u1ec1n ngu\\u1ed3n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng l\\u1edbn, t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 19-4, V\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u01b0\\u01a1m Doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng (DNES) tri\\u1ec3n khai ti\\u1ebfp nh\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u01a1n \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd cho ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cB\\u1ec7 ph\\u00f3ng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d d\\u00e0nh cho \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean n\\u0103m 2022. Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh do Th\\u00e0nh \\u0110o\\u00e0n \\u0110\\u00e0 N\\u1eb5ng ph\\u1ed1i h\\u1ee3p DNES t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c v\\u00e0o ng\\u00e0y 23, 24-4-2022.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Theo \\u0111\\u00f3, \\u0111\\u1ed1i t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng tham gia l\\u00e0 t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 sinh vi\\u00ean y\\u00eau th\\u00edch kinh doanh, kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111ang theo h\\u1ecdc t\\u1ea1i c\\u00e1c tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc, cao \\u0111\\u1eb3ng tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh g\\u1ed3m 2 giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n: Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 1 l\\u00e0 Bootcamp (kh\\u1edfi \\u0111\\u1ed9ng) \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c trong 2 ng\\u00e0y 23 v\\u00e0 24-4 v\\u1edbi 50 \\u0111o\\u00e0n vi\\u00ean. Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n n\\u00e0y gi\\u00fap c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n v\\u1ec1 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; X\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5u hi\\u1ec3u v\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; Hi\\u1ec3u r\\u00f5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u00e2n dung c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00e0 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng; Ki\\u1ec3m ch\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p kh\\u1ea3 thi.<\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><a class=\\\"dng-img-viewer\\\" style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/21-4%20VUON%20UOM.jpg\\\"><img class=\\\"image_resized\\\" style=\\\"width:695px;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.portal.danang.gov.vn\\/images\\/images\\/Nam%202022\\/Thang%2004\\/21-4%20VUON%20UOM.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"><\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">Giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 2 l\\u00e0 Incubator (\\u01b0\\u01a1m t\\u1ea1o) g\\u1ed3m 3 c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n ho\\u1eb7c nh\\u00f3m xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qua giai \\u0111o\\u1ea1n 1. C\\u00e1c c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n ho\\u1eb7c nh\\u00f3m s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o chuy\\u00ean s\\u00e2u d\\u01b0\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ed1 v\\u1ea5n 1 k\\u00e8m 1 c\\u1ee7a chuy\\u00ean gia \\u0111\\u1ed3ng h\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111i s\\u00e2u v\\u00e0o x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng m\\u00f4 h\\u00ecnh kinh doanh kh\\u1ea3 thi. \\u0110\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi, 3 c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n\\/nh\\u00f3m xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t c\\u00f2n c\\u00f3 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i tham gia chuy\\u1ebfn tham quan StartUp Tour; tham quan tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf ch\\u00ednh v\\u00e0 giao l\\u01b0u tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp v\\u1edbi c\\u00e1c StartUp tri\\u1ec7u \\u0111\\u00f4; Chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb s\\u1eb5n s\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 tham gia v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c cu\\u1ed9c thi kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p. \\u0110\\u0103ng k\\u00fd tham gia t\\u1ea1i link:&nbsp;<a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/forms.gle\\/iNfvWnZZaTrm62L47\\\">https:\\/\\/forms.gle\\/iNfvWnZZaTrm62L47<\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:justify;word-spacing:0px;\\\">B\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh DNES, Trung t\\u00e2m \\u01b0\\u01a1m t\\u1ea1o Kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p S\\u00f4ng H\\u00e0n (Songhan incubator) c\\u0169ng v\\u1eeba ra m\\u1eaft ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh Songhan incubator - Startup Internship Program (SHi \\u2013 SIP 2022). Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0 c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho c\\u00e1c b\\u1ea1n sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn v\\u00e0 tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m th\\u1ef1c t\\u1ebf v\\u1edbi l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi s\\u00e1ng t\\u1ea1o. C\\u00e1c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ch\\u00ednh c\\u1ee7a ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0 k\\u1ebft n\\u1ed1i startup v\\u00e0 sinh vi\\u00ean, sinh vi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp b\\u1edfi c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia c\\u00f3 nhi\\u1ec1u n\\u0103m kinh nghi\\u1ec7m trong l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c chuy\\u00ean m\\u00f4n. \\u0110\\u0103ng k\\u00fd tham gia t\\u1ea1i <a style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(51,122,183);text-decoration:none;\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/forms.office.com\\/r\\/9PfjV8Fpgi\\\">https:\\/\\/forms.office.com\\/r\\/9PfjV8Fpgi.<\\/a><\\/p><p style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;text-align:right;word-spacing:0px;\\\"><strong>NGUY\\u00caN TH\\u1ea2O - https:\\/\\/danang.gov.vn\\/<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"8\"],\"image\":\"news\\/21-4-vuon-uom.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep sang tao\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"sinh vien\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"sinh vien khoi nghiep\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/101.0.4951.54 Safari/537.36', '14.241.81.27', 1, 2, 'Nhiều hoạt động hỗ trợ sinh viên khởi nghiệp', 'primary', '2022-05-17 00:49:26', '2022-05-17 00:49:26'),
(434, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d t\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai\",\"slug\":\"tin-tuc-cafe-khoi-nghiep-tao-dung-tuong-lai\",\"slug_id\":\"85\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":\"H\\u1ed9i Li\\u00ean hi\\u1ec7p Ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef (LHPN) TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh v\\u1eeba t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p-Chia s\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1ec3 v\\u01b0\\u01a1n cao\\u201d.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh thu h\\u00fat \\u0111\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ea3o h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 h\\u00e0o h\\u1ee9ng tham gia \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ti\\u1ebfp thu, chia s\\u1ebb ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c, kinh nghi\\u1ec7m, h\\u01b0\\u1edbng d\\u1eabn k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.qdnd.vn\\/giao-duc-khoa-hoc\\/cac-van-de\\/khoi-nghiep-lan-song-moi-trong-gioi-tre-690081\\\">kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p<\\/a>, ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">V\\u1edbi nh\\u1eefng th\\u00f4ng tin b\\u1ed5 \\u00edch v\\u1ec1 kinh doanh online;&nbsp;k\\u1ef9 n\\u0103ng, chi\\u1ebfn l\\u01b0\\u1ee3c kinh doanh trong th\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ea1i s\\u1ed1; huy \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1ed1n kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p; t\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng uy t\\u00edn, th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u..., c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia, di\\u1ec5n gi\\u1ea3, doanh nh\\u00e2n th\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u201ctruy\\u1ec1n l\\u1eeda\\u201d gi\\u00fap h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef t\\u1ef1 tin kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p trong b\\u1ed1i c\\u1ea3nh c\\u1ea1nh tranh v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed9i nh\\u1eadp.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Ngay sau ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c c\\u1ea5p th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1, H\\u1ed9i LHPN c\\u00e1c qu\\u1eadn, huy\\u1ec7n nhanh ch\\u00f3ng tri\\u1ec3n khai r\\u1ed9ng kh\\u1eafp tr\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n, l\\u00e0m d\\u1ea5y l\\u00ean tinh th\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p t\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai.<\\/p><figure class=\\\"image\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/file3.qdnd.vn\\/data\\/images\\/0\\/2022\\/03\\/29\\/nguyenthao\\/cafe%20khoi%20nghiep.jpg?dpi=150&amp;quality=100&amp;w=870\\\" alt=\\\"\\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d t\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai\\\"><\\/figure><p style=\\\"text-align:center;\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(236,236,236);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:13px;\\\"><span>H\\u1ed9i Li\\u00ean hi\\u1ec7p ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh trao v\\u1ed1n cho h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean kinh doanh kh\\u00f3 kh\\u0103n do Covid-19. \\u1ea2nh: Voh.vn&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><br>&nbsp;Th\\u1ef1c ra, ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c H\\u1ed9i LHPN th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 th\\u00ed \\u0111i\\u1ec3m th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1eeb qu\\u00fd II-2019 nh\\u1eb1m \\u0111\\u1ecbnh h\\u01b0\\u1edbng, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3, ti\\u1ebfp s\\u1ee9c cho c\\u00e1c d\\u1ef1 \\u00e1n, m\\u00f4 h\\u00ecnh kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p do h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, do th\\u1eddi gian d\\u1ecbch Covid-19 k\\u00e9o d\\u00e0i n\\u00ean ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh t\\u1ea1m l\\u1eafng, \\u0111\\u1ebfn nay m\\u1edbi ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Theo th\\u1ed1ng k\\u00ea c\\u1ee7a H\\u1ed9i LHPN th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1, t\\u00ednh \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m n\\u00e0y, th\\u00f4ng qua Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d, c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea5p h\\u1ed9i ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef \\u0111\\u00e3 h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3, ti\\u1ebfp s\\u1ee9c cho h\\u00e0ng ngh\\u00ecn h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean m\\u1ea1nh d\\u1ea1n th\\u1eed s\\u1ee9c trong c\\u00e1c l\\u0129nh v\\u1ef1c s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh, v\\u01b0\\u01a1n l\\u00ean l\\u00e0m gi\\u00e0u v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3p t\\u00edch c\\u1ef1c cho c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Theo k\\u1ebft qu\\u1ea3 \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tra x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i h\\u1ecdc, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef Vi\\u1ec7t Nam n\\u00f3i chung, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef TP H\\u1ed3 Ch\\u00ed Minh n\\u00f3i ri\\u00eang \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u1ed1i m\\u1eb7t v\\u1edbi nhi\\u1ec1u r\\u00e0o c\\u1ea3n trong kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, nh\\u01b0: Ti\\u1ebfp c\\u1eadn t\\u00e0i ch\\u00ednh, \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ki\\u1ebfn x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i, thi\\u1ebfu t\\u1ef1 tin, ch\\u01b0a quy\\u1ebft \\u0111o\\u00e1n trong qu\\u1ea3n l\\u00fd, \\u0111i\\u1ec1u h\\u00e0nh doanh nghi\\u1ec7p...<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">B\\u1edfi v\\u1eady, \\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d ch\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 n\\u01a1i gi\\u00fap ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t qua nh\\u1eefng r\\u00e0o c\\u1ea3n \\u0111\\u00f3 m\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n ph\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ea3i qua nh\\u1eefng l\\u1edbp \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o ch\\u00ednh quy, b\\u00e0i b\\u1ea3n. Nh\\u1eefng ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c th\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ec5n, kinh nghi\\u1ec7m, b\\u00ed quy\\u1ebft kinh doanh m\\u00e0 c\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia, doanh nh\\u00e2n th\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ea1t chia s\\u1ebb th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1 b\\u1ed5 \\u00edch, h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef m\\u1ea1nh d\\u1ea1n h\\u01a1n tr\\u00ean con \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u1eadp nghi\\u1ec7p, kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, qu\\u1ea3n tr\\u1ecb doanh nghi\\u1ec7p, ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh t\\u1ed1t h\\u01a1n, hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 h\\u01a1n; \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi gi\\u1ea3i quy\\u1ebft th\\u1ecfa \\u0111\\u00e1ng c\\u00e1c t\\u00ecnh hu\\u1ed1ng kh\\u00f3 trong kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p kinh doanh.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">V\\u1edbi m\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u00edch&nbsp;chia s\\u1ebb, trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i, gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u v\\u00e0 \\u201c\\u0111\\u1ee1 \\u0111\\u1ea7u\\u201d c\\u00e1c \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kinh doanh ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf, Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh di\\u1ec5n \\u0111\\u00e0n d\\u00e0nh cho h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef c\\u00f3 nhu c\\u1ea7u kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, kh\\u1edfi s\\u1ef1 kinh doanh. Ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c trong kh\\u00f4ng gian m\\u1edf, kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00e2u n\\u1ec7 th\\u1ec3 th\\u1ee9c, t\\u1ea1o s\\u1ef1 g\\u1ea7n g\\u0169i, th\\u00e2n thi\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 g\\u1eafn k\\u1ebft.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">C\\u00e1c chuy\\u00ean gia, doanh nh\\u00e2n th\\u00e0nh \\u0111\\u1ea1t v\\u00e0 h\\u1ed9i vi\\u00ean, ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef \\u0111\\u1ee7 m\\u1ecdi th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ea7n, l\\u1ee9a tu\\u1ed5i tho\\u1ea3i m\\u00e1i chia s\\u1ebb \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eadn v\\u1ec1 nh\\u1eefng l\\u1eddi khuy\\u00ean ch\\u00e2n th\\u00e0nh, thi\\u1ebft th\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea3o \\u0111\\u1ea3m cho \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">C\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c truy\\u1ec1n c\\u1ea3m h\\u1ee9ng v\\u00e0 ki\\u1ebfn th\\u1ee9c, kinh nghi\\u1ec7m kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p, nh\\u1eefng \\u00fd t\\u01b0\\u1edfng kh\\u1ea3 thi nh\\u01b0ng ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u00e2n thi\\u1ebfu v\\u1ed1n s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea5p h\\u1ed9i ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 kinh ph\\u00ed ho\\u1eb7c gi\\u1edbi thi\\u1ec7u, b\\u1ea3o l\\u00e3nh ngu\\u1ed3n vay \\u0111\\u1ec3 kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p...&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">B\\u1edfi v\\u1eady, \\u201cC\\u00e0 ph\\u00ea kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p\\u201d th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1 l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh b\\u1ed5 \\u00edch, c\\u00f3 s\\u1ee9c lan t\\u1ecfa m\\u1ea1nh m\\u1ebd, th\\u1ed5i lu\\u1ed3ng sinh kh\\u00ed kh\\u1edfi nghi\\u1ec7p s\\u1ea3n xu\\u1ea5t, kinh doanh, kh\\u00edch l\\u1ec7 ph\\u1ee5 n\\u1eef th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 t\\u1ef1 tin kh\\u1eb3ng \\u0111\\u1ecbnh m\\u00ecnh, t\\u1ea1o d\\u1ef1ng t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai, c\\u00f9ng nhau v\\u01b0\\u01a1n l\\u00ean l\\u00e0m gi\\u00e0u cho gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00f3ng g\\u00f3p cho c\\u1ed9ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:right;\\\"><strong>CH\\u00c2U GIANG - QU\\u00c2N \\u0110\\u1ed8I NH\\u00c2N D\\u00c2N.<\\/strong><\\/p><h4>&nbsp;<\\/h4><p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"vi\",\"status\":\"published\",\"categories\":[\"8\"],\"image\":\"news\\/cpkn-2018-btaskee-10-100-00-39-10still001.jpg\",\"tag\":\"[{\\\"value\\\":\\\"khoi nghiep\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"startup\\\"},{\\\"value\\\":\\\"phu nu khoi nghiep\\\"}]\"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/101.0.4951.54 Safari/537.36', '14.241.81.27', 1, 3, 'Chương trình “Cà phê khởi nghiệp” tạo dựng tương lai', 'primary', '2022-05-17 00:49:38', '2022-05-17 00:49:38');
