(554, 1, 'post', '{\"name\":\"C\\u1ea9m nang Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1\",\"slug\":\"cam-nang\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"is_slug_editable\":\"1\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Blog\\\\Models\\\\Post\",\"description\":null,\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:13.0pt;\\\">C\\u1ea9m nang Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c B\\u1ed9 Th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u00e0 Truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng ph\\u00e1t h\\u00e0nh d\\u01b0\\u1edbi d\\u1ea1ng s\\u00e1ch v\\u00e0 phi\\u00ean b\\u1ea3n \\u0111i\\u1ec7n t\\u1eed, g\\u00f3i g\\u1ecdn qua c\\u00e1c c\\u00e2u h\\u1ecfi - c\\u00e2u tr\\u1ea3 l\\u1eddi c\\u00f9ng nhi\\u1ec1u v\\u00ed d\\u1ee5 minh h\\u1ecda.Hi\\u1ec7n nay, chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 \\u0111ang l\\u00e0 xu th\\u1ebf t\\u1ea5t y\\u1ebfu tr\\u00ean to\\u00e0n c\\u1ea7u, m\\u1edf ra c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i ch\\u01b0a t\\u1eebng c\\u00f3 cho Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ee9t ph\\u00e1 v\\u01b0\\u01a1n l\\u00ean, thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i th\\u1ee9 h\\u1ea1ng qu\\u1ed1c gia.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:13.0pt;\\\">Ng\\u00e0y 3\\/6\\/2020, Th\\u1ee7 t\\u01b0\\u1edbng Ch\\u00ednh ph\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u00e3 ban h\\u00e0nh Quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh s\\u1ed1 749\\/Q\\u0110-TTg ph\\u00ea duy\\u1ec7t ch\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u00ecnh Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 qu\\u1ed1c gia \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u0103m 2025, \\u0111\\u1ecbnh h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u0103m 2030. B\\u1ed9 Th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u00e0 Truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 d\\u1eabn d\\u1eaft chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 qu\\u1ed1c gia bao g\\u1ed3m 3 tr\\u1ee5 c\\u1ed9t l\\u00e0 Ch\\u00ednh ph\\u1ee7 s\\u1ed1, kinh t\\u1ebf s\\u1ed1 v\\u00e0 x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i s\\u1ed1.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:13.0pt;\\\">D\\u00f9 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u1eeb nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ed9t ph\\u00e1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 s\\u1ed1 nh\\u01b0ng chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 l\\u1ea1i kh\\u00f4ng ph\\u1ea3i ch\\u1ec9 l\\u00e0 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7 s\\u1ed1 m\\u00e0 quan tr\\u1ecdng h\\u01a1n, chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 l\\u00e0 ch\\u1ea5p nh\\u1eadn c\\u00e1i m\\u1edbi. Ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec v\\u1eady, chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 l\\u00e0 cu\\u1ed9c c\\u00e1ch m\\u1ea1ng v\\u1ec1 nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ee9c nhi\\u1ec1u h\\u01a1n l\\u00e0 cu\\u1ed9c c\\u00e1ch m\\u1ea1ng v\\u1ec1 c\\u00f4ng ngh\\u1ec7.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:13.0pt;\\\">Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ee9c v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ee9 m\\u1ec7nh, s\\u1ef1 c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft, t\\u00ednh c\\u1ea5p b\\u00e1ch c\\u1ee7a chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1 trong x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i, v\\u1edbi mong mu\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u1ebfn ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n v\\u00e0 doanh nghi\\u1ec7p nh\\u1eefng \\u0111i\\u1ec1u quan tr\\u1ecdng v\\u00e0 thi\\u1ebft y\\u1ebfu v\\u1ec1 chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1, B\\u1ed9 Th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u00e0 Truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u00e3 x\\u00e2y d\\u1ef1ng v\\u00e0 ho\\u00e0n thi\\u1ec7n C\\u1ea9m nang Chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i s\\u1ed1.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p style=\\\"margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:black;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box;font-size:13.0pt;\\\">C\\u1ea9m nang